    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You unleash a scream of hatred and violence against all those who have wronged you. Each creature of your choosing within 10ft of you must make a Wisdom saving throw, on a failed save they become Dazed, Deafened and gain 1 rank of Fear.</p><p><em><strong>Violent Vice.</strong></em> As part of casting this jutsu, you may spend up to 1 <strong>Vice Point</strong>. If you do, creatures within 5 feet of you roll at disadvantage.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank above D-Rank, this Jutsu costs 3 more chakra, and increases its range by 10ft.</p>",
